Опис вакансії
Our Company provides the highest standards of compliance and verification: Email Support Services/ Customer Care Services/ Chat Support Services/ Programmatic digital media services Business relationships are as diverse as the services we render. Today we proudly serve hundreds of customers in more than 30 countries, spanning 4 continents. Responsibilities: • Verification specialist; • Compliance and customer support team; • Developing, implementing and managing of companies' compliance program; • Performing the due diligence on new Clients, requesting information, documentation, review and verification of received documentation and making an analytical risk assessment for new Clients; • Periodically evaluate existing Clients according to established policies and procedures; • Periodical review of documents records as to completeness, including verifying that due diligence has been performed; • Process entries to open/close clients' account on our KYC / Related Parties and database; • Communicate effectively and efficiently with relevant internal and external parties to obtain documents; • Perform further investigation on identified suspicious client and client’s transactions and report to management.Requirements: • STRONG written and verbal communications skills in English (Advanced); • Good PC skills; • Personal qualities: — diligent and disciplined; — diligent to deadlines; — quick learner.The Company offers: • Competitive position in a fast-paced working environment; • Career and professional opportunities; • Shift work schedule; • Possibility to work on challenging tasks in multinational team of professionals; • Cozy and comfortable office; • Friendly team. Send your CV to our Email, or call us! HR-manager Yuliia
